WEBVTT

00:01:35.680 --> 00:01:36.959
What's going on with Xiaofeng?

00:01:37.200 --> 00:01:39.040
This person brought a fake bag to return.

00:01:39.040 --> 00:01:40.359
No, I... I...

00:01:40.359 --> 00:01:41.959
Okay, okay, um, I...

00:01:41.959 --> 00:01:42.959
I'll leave the bag here as collateral.

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:44.599
I'll bring you the real bag, okay?

00:01:44.599 --> 00:01:45.439
Don't leave yet.

00:01:47.120 --> 00:01:49.280
If you... if you don't believe me, then I'll have to...

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.400
Otherwise... otherwise I'll call... call the police.

00:01:50.400 --> 00:01:52.719
Let the police... the officers clear my name.

00:01:52.719 --> 00:01:53.840
Is that okay with you?

00:01:56.959 --> 00:01:57.799
I'll call them myself.

00:02:25.479 --> 00:02:28.080
Driver, we're not going to Baofang Hutong anymore.

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:29.360
I'll change the address.

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:30.479
Alright, go ahead and change it.

00:02:46.319 --> 00:02:47.479
What happened?

00:02:47.479 --> 00:02:49.000
Why didn't you look more carefully?

00:02:49.319 --> 00:02:51.800
You made Xiaoshi come all this way for nothing.

00:02:53.120 --> 00:02:55.479
That fake was made exactly like the real one.

00:02:56.639 --> 00:02:58.120
An ordinary person really couldn't tell the difference.

00:02:58.120 --> 00:02:59.919
Luckily, the misunderstanding was cleared up.

00:02:59.919 --> 00:03:00.919
And the bag was returned.

00:03:01.199 --> 00:03:02.080
Have some dumplings.

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:03.759
Go ahead, eat.

00:03:03.759 --> 00:03:05.560
Eat more, you must be hungry.

00:03:07.199 --> 00:03:08.000
Xiaoshi.

00:03:08.400 --> 00:03:10.159
Since you've come back with such difficulty,

00:03:10.280 --> 00:03:12.280
stay a few more days before leaving.

00:03:12.479 --> 00:03:14.080
I applied for a job rotation.

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:15.439
So I can come back and stay for a while.

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:16.199
Good.

00:03:16.199 --> 00:03:17.560
That's good then.

00:03:17.639 --> 00:03:19.719
I tell you, you young people...

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:21.919
Why are you all so busy?

00:03:25.080 --> 00:03:25.919
Look,

00:03:26.919 --> 00:03:28.159
as for me,

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:31.199
I got you some more traditional medicine.

00:03:31.199 --> 00:03:33.479
Tonic medicine. This is tonic medicine.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:36.199
I originally wanted to mail it to you,

00:03:36.479 --> 00:03:37.759
but since you're back now,

00:03:37.759 --> 00:03:38.879
it's perfect timing.

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:40.639
You have to remember,

00:03:40.639 --> 00:03:44.199
take one dose every morning and evening.

00:03:44.759 --> 00:03:46.039
Okay, Mom.

00:03:46.599 --> 00:03:47.759
You have to drink it too.

00:03:49.039 --> 00:03:51.159
You're the one who needs it most.

00:03:52.639 --> 00:03:55.319
What's going on with you two?

00:03:55.319 --> 00:03:56.479
It's been so long,

00:03:56.479 --> 00:03:57.680
and there's still no news.

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.080
Mom, then I suggest don't give me the medicine.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.639
Just grill me two big kidneys tonight.

00:04:01.639 --> 00:04:03.039
What are you talking about?

00:04:07.680 --> 00:04:08.960
Tell Weiguo to do it.

00:04:11.479 --> 00:04:12.919
Why call him?

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:15.199
No, how can you talk like that?

00:04:15.199 --> 00:04:16.319
Alright, enough.

00:04:16.600 --> 00:04:18.839
Don't meddle so much in the kids' business.

00:04:19.360 --> 00:04:20.639
What's going on with you and Third Brother?

00:04:25.199 --> 00:04:26.759
Come on, come on, eat dumplings, eat dumplings.

00:04:26.759 --> 00:04:27.759
Eat, eat, eat.

00:04:27.759 --> 00:04:28.480
They're delicious.

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:29.279
Want some vinegar?

00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:30.439
Have some.

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:45.560
Shi, I really envy you.

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.839
Ever since I married your Boss,

00:04:47.839 --> 00:04:50.120
I've been revolving around Peng Le Xuan every day.

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:52.800
I'm busy to death every day.

00:04:53.879 --> 00:04:57.120
And have no time to go out and see the world.

00:04:57.399 --> 00:04:59.000
Auntie, please don't say that.

00:04:59.279 --> 00:05:01.560
I think Peng Le Xuan is your domain.

00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:03.240
If you weren't here,

00:05:03.240 --> 00:05:04.839
could Uncle Wang handle it alone?

00:05:04.839 --> 00:05:05.399
He absolutely couldn't.

00:05:05.399 --> 00:05:06.240
Exactly.

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:08.560
See, Tongtong knows how to talk.

00:05:13.399 --> 00:05:17.279
Shi'er, I've always been too embarrassed to ask you...

00:05:17.480 --> 00:05:18.800
But today it's just the three of us.

00:05:19.319 --> 00:05:23.240
Do you and Tongqiu plan to have children or not?

00:05:23.519 --> 00:05:25.399
You've been married for so many years now.

00:05:25.399 --> 00:05:26.720
From my experience,

00:05:27.000 --> 00:05:28.720
if you want them, have them early.

00:05:30.959 --> 00:05:32.519
We do want them now.

00:05:32.519 --> 00:05:33.879
Really?

00:05:36.079 --> 00:05:36.959
Auntie.

00:05:36.959 --> 00:05:39.319
Before, I heard you and Uncle Qiu'er were going to be DINKs.

00:05:39.319 --> 00:05:40.319
Not having children.

00:05:40.720 --> 00:05:43.279
Was it because of Grandpa and Grandma's pressure?

00:05:44.879 --> 00:05:45.879
No.

00:05:46.759 --> 00:05:48.439
It was because of my father-in-law's illness.

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:53.560
These past two years we've been running to the hospital a lot.

00:05:55.319 --> 00:05:55.959
You know,

00:05:55.959 --> 00:05:57.759
what I encountered most often?

00:05:58.959 --> 00:06:01.160
Many elderly people without children accompanying them.

00:06:01.319 --> 00:06:02.879
They don't know how to make appointments on their phones.

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:04.759
Don't know how to use the registration machines.

00:06:04.759 --> 00:06:06.959
Don't know how to scan codes to get lab reports.

00:06:06.959 --> 00:06:08.720
And certainly don't know electronic payment.

00:06:09.279 --> 00:06:11.879
We young people find this digitalization very convenient,

00:06:11.959 --> 00:06:14.759
but for the elderly, these are all problems.

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:16.399
You're right about that.

00:06:17.399 --> 00:06:18.519
Just these newfangled things,

00:06:18.519 --> 00:06:20.079
even now I can't figure them out.

00:06:20.079 --> 00:06:20.879
Right.

00:06:21.199 --> 00:06:22.879
When my father-in-law was hospitalized,

00:06:22.959 --> 00:06:24.319
the elderly in the ward,

00:06:24.639 --> 00:06:26.079
some had tubes inserted,

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:27.639
some were on ventilators.

00:06:27.639 --> 00:06:28.959
They couldn't get out of bed.

00:06:29.439 --> 00:06:31.079
Eating, drinking, and relieving themselves all in bed.

00:06:31.319 --> 00:06:33.879
Just the incontinence pads had to be changed several times a day.

00:06:34.600 --> 00:06:35.839
So I thought,

00:06:36.279 --> 00:06:37.839
right now my father-in-law

00:06:38.199 --> 00:06:39.759
still has the two of us to care for him.

00:06:40.839 --> 00:06:43.199
But in the future, when Tongqiu and I are old,

00:06:43.519 --> 00:06:45.199
if we have no children,

00:06:46.079 --> 00:06:47.319
what will we do?

00:06:48.759 --> 00:06:51.399
So you decided to have children because of this?

00:06:55.639 --> 00:06:56.959
It might sound...

00:06:57.319 --> 00:06:58.720
pretty selfish.

00:06:59.639 --> 00:07:01.759
But this is truly my real thought.

00:07:03.839 --> 00:07:05.319
But if a child is born

00:07:05.519 --> 00:07:07.439
and knows their parents originally thought this way,

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:09.399
they would surely be very hurt.

00:07:10.720 --> 00:07:12.199
If I had a child,

00:07:12.319 --> 00:07:13.879
I would definitely love them very much.

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:16.000
That doesn't conflict.

00:07:17.959 --> 00:07:19.519
But what if they aren't filial?

00:07:22.079 --> 00:07:23.519
You two are getting off track.

00:07:24.279 --> 00:07:25.959
Whether they're filial or not is a separate issue.

00:07:26.199 --> 00:07:28.199
First, you have to have the child.

00:07:28.959 --> 00:07:29.639
Also,

00:07:29.639 --> 00:07:30.879
Look at Wang Fei now.

00:07:31.439 --> 00:07:33.519
Just this one matter of going to university

00:07:33.759 --> 00:07:35.079
has me and your Boss

00:07:35.079 --> 00:07:36.519
in a constant uproar all day long.

00:07:36.519 --> 00:07:38.079
We still haven't figured it out.

00:07:38.279 --> 00:07:40.079
So don't overthink it.

00:07:40.079 --> 00:07:41.079
Just get pregnant first.

00:07:44.120 --> 00:07:45.920
I even want two.

00:07:46.240 --> 00:07:47.519
Twins.

00:07:47.639 --> 00:07:48.399
I support that.

00:07:48.439 --> 00:07:48.959
Here.

00:07:48.959 --> 00:07:49.879
Come on, come on.

00:07:50.040 --> 00:07:51.079
Come on, come on.

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:53.439
Hope you have twins.

00:07:53.439 --> 00:07:54.040
It's definitely possible.

00:07:54.040 --> 00:07:54.759
You can do it.

00:08:02.639 --> 00:08:05.639
Hearing you say that, I admire Third Brother even more.

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:13.439
Third Brother has strategy and skill.

00:08:13.639 --> 00:08:15.839
No wonder they say he's had lots of ideas since he was little.

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:18.279
No wonder he's made it big in the US.

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:22.759
Look at you with those starry eyes.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:25.120
The more capable someone is, the more trouble they can cause.

00:08:27.079 --> 00:08:30.120
He hasn't done anything particularly terrible, has he?

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:31.439
Besides,

00:08:31.600 --> 00:08:32.759
When it comes to business,

00:08:32.759 --> 00:08:35.039
you have to separate it from personal feelings.

00:08:37.000 --> 00:08:38.120
Originally,

00:08:38.440 --> 00:08:41.240
I was quite worried about you running Peng Le Xuan together.

00:08:41.559 --> 00:08:43.320
But now with Third Brother involved,

00:08:43.320 --> 00:08:45.000
I think it's a sure thing!

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:47.000
A sure thing!

00:08:47.559 --> 00:08:48.759
This... this is a sure thing?

00:08:48.759 --> 00:08:49.679
Sure... sure thing.

00:08:49.679 --> 00:08:51.000
Sure, sure, sure.

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.519
Sure, sure, sure thing.

00:08:53.879 --> 00:08:55.120
That "sure thing" sounds too convincing.

00:08:57.000 --> 00:08:57.639
You haven't seen

00:08:57.639 --> 00:08:59.240
how much trouble he's caused us.

00:08:59.639 --> 00:09:01.240
He drove Boss to that state,

00:09:01.759 --> 00:09:03.559
and keeps insisting I quit my job.

00:09:06.759 --> 00:09:07.559
Honey,

00:09:08.240 --> 00:09:09.519
think about it carefully.

00:09:09.879 --> 00:09:11.320
What he says makes some sense.

00:09:11.320 --> 00:09:13.000
You can't have your cake and eat it too.

00:09:13.679 --> 00:09:14.879
If you try to ride two horses at once,

00:09:14.879 --> 00:09:16.440
you'll fall sooner or later.

00:09:19.480 --> 00:09:20.799
Third Brother is so capable.

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:23.519
You have a chance to start a business with him now.

00:09:25.960 --> 00:09:28.159
It might suit you better than the bank in the long run.

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:30.840
At least you won't earn less money.

00:09:31.320 --> 00:09:32.879
What do you say we give it a try?

00:09:32.879 --> 00:09:34.200
Listen to Third Brother.

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:35.879
Stop, just stop.

00:09:35.879 --> 00:09:39.120
You can't just quit a job on a whim.

00:09:39.559 --> 00:09:41.080
And whether I'll work with him

00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:41.879
is still up in the air.

00:09:42.639 --> 00:09:44.799
Don't be so emotional.

00:09:46.559 --> 00:09:47.759
I think Third Brother's

00:09:48.240 --> 00:09:50.240
approach to handling things is quite right.

00:09:50.320 --> 00:09:51.600
His approach is right,

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:53.000
but he can't be heartless either.

00:09:54.000 --> 00:09:56.519
Asking you to think about the future is heartless?

00:09:56.519 --> 00:09:58.519
Are you taking his side now?

00:09:58.519 --> 00:09:59.720
Whose side are you on, anyway?

00:09:59.720 --> 00:10:01.000
I'm your husband!

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:04.360
And now it's all money, money, money every day.

00:10:04.360 --> 00:10:05.360
Is there nothing else in our lives

00:10:05.360 --> 00:10:06.759
besides money?

00:10:23.120 --> 00:10:25.000
Mom, wife,

00:10:26.600 --> 00:10:28.360
I have some great news to announce.

00:10:29.639 --> 00:10:31.000
We have a house!

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:32.240
A big house!

00:10:32.519 --> 00:10:34.000
A villa, actually!

00:10:34.360 --> 00:10:35.639
A villa!

00:10:39.080 --> 00:10:41.679
If I had accepted Weiguo's villa back then,

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:43.799
would things be different?

00:10:57.840 --> 00:10:59.759
Qiu'er, Qiu'er.

00:11:00.600 --> 00:11:01.960
What's wrong?

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:03.600
You look all wilted.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:05.120
Like you've lost your soul.

00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:06.240
It's nothing, nothing.

00:11:06.240 --> 00:11:08.240
Nothing? That can't be right.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:09.600
Nothing, really, it's nothing.

00:11:09.720 --> 00:11:12.360
If it's nothing, why are you sweating so much? What's going on?

00:11:12.360 --> 00:11:13.200
Re-really, it's nothing.

00:11:13.200 --> 00:11:13.759
There's definitely something.

00:11:13.759 --> 00:11:14.360
Nothing.

00:11:15.759 --> 00:11:16.600
There really is something.

00:11:16.600 --> 00:11:18.360
There is something. You...

00:11:18.360 --> 00:11:19.240
Let's talk at home.

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:19.879
Let's talk when we get home.

00:11:19.879 --> 00:11:20.360
Alright, alright.

00:11:20.360 --> 00:11:20.840
This is no place to talk.

00:11:20.840 --> 00:11:21.759
Talk at home, talk at home.

00:11:21.759 --> 00:11:22.240
Let's go.

00:11:29.879 --> 00:11:33.000
I've already found that chef.

00:11:33.360 --> 00:11:34.600
It's still that Chef Sun.

00:11:35.519 --> 00:11:37.159
He agreed to sign the contract soon.

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:39.240
I also had him sign up for

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:40.600
this year's Duck King Competition.

00:11:41.960 --> 00:11:43.279
No need to be in such a hurry, right?

00:11:43.559 --> 00:11:44.679
Let's wait for Boss a bit longer.

00:11:45.200 --> 00:11:46.679
Time waits for no one.

00:11:46.960 --> 00:11:49.320
Registration closes in less than a week.

00:11:52.159 --> 00:11:53.159
But if the roast duck

00:11:53.159 --> 00:11:54.960
isn't made by Boss himself,

00:11:55.200 --> 00:11:56.080
then for Peng Le Xuan,

00:11:56.080 --> 00:11:57.320
it holds no meaning at all.

00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:09.120
Let me be honest with you.

00:12:09.440 --> 00:12:11.559
The money I secured comes with conditions.

00:12:12.559 --> 00:12:13.679
Within six months,

00:12:13.679 --> 00:12:14.679
Peng Le Xuan must be

00:12:14.679 --> 00:12:16.679
pushed into the top ten on all major platforms.

00:12:18.039 --> 00:12:18.960
The only chance

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:20.840
is to win this year's Duck King Competition.

00:12:21.559 --> 00:12:23.440
That's why I'm set on Chef Sun.

00:12:23.879 --> 00:12:25.240
He was the runner-up last time.

00:12:25.679 --> 00:12:27.799
The last champion, due to his age,

00:12:27.799 --> 00:12:29.600
has announced he won't compete anymore.

00:12:30.879 --> 00:12:32.080
So for this championship,

00:12:32.080 --> 00:12:33.559
Chef Sun has a very high probability.

00:12:34.639 --> 00:12:35.799
With Boss in his current state,

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.240
what else can I do?

00:12:39.200 --> 00:12:42.480
What if Chef Sun doesn't win the championship?

00:12:42.799 --> 00:12:43.960
He must win.

00:12:44.039 --> 00:12:45.320
I have no other way out.

00:12:51.080 --> 00:12:53.440
You mustn't tell Boss and Qiu'er about this.

00:12:54.159 --> 00:12:55.559
They can't handle the pressure.

00:12:56.200 --> 00:12:57.919
Especially with Boss like he is now.

00:12:58.320 --> 00:12:59.320
If we put more pressure on him,

00:12:59.320 --> 00:13:00.559
he simply won't be able to take it.

00:13:02.440 --> 00:13:04.440
Having Chef Sun step in to replace him now

00:13:04.960 --> 00:13:06.080
might actually be a good thing.

00:13:09.440 --> 00:13:11.240
Getting Boss back on his feet

00:13:11.679 --> 00:13:13.440
isn't just for Peng Le Xuan's sake.

00:13:13.840 --> 00:13:15.080
It's even more for his own sake.

00:13:16.200 --> 00:13:18.159
If he can't pull himself together,

00:13:18.559 --> 00:13:20.320
what will he do with the rest of his life?

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:23.440
I can't worry about that much anymore.

00:13:23.919 --> 00:13:25.559
We'll deal with the future later.

00:13:42.000 --> 00:13:42.759
Boss.

00:13:43.120 --> 00:13:44.960
Weiguo and I have discussed it.

00:13:45.240 --> 00:13:46.759
We still need to hire a chef.

00:13:47.080 --> 00:13:48.240
So we won't trouble you anymore.

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:51.960
It's still that Sun guy, isn't it?

00:13:55.240 --> 00:13:56.000
Chunsheng.

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:56.879
Boss.

00:13:57.360 --> 00:13:59.080
I'm doing this for Peng Le Xuan's good too.

00:13:59.600 --> 00:14:00.840
And that Chef Sun

00:14:00.840 --> 00:14:02.840
can also help Peng Le Xuan take a big step forward.

00:14:02.960 --> 00:14:04.120
Just trust me this once.

00:14:06.399 --> 00:14:07.279
Um,

00:14:07.279 --> 00:14:09.399
Peng Le Xuan's renovation officially starts tomorrow.

00:14:10.159 --> 00:14:12.519
Before work begins, there's a Signboard Removal Ceremony.

00:14:12.840 --> 00:14:15.240
You and Sister-in-law must come.

00:14:17.519 --> 00:14:19.120
Well, if there's nothing else, I'll head off now.

00:14:23.360 --> 00:14:25.480
That's fine. Go ahead.

00:14:26.080 --> 00:14:28.360
You'll have one less worry from now on.

00:14:38.000 --> 00:14:41.080
Your roast duck restaurant, with Peng Le Xuan's backing,

00:14:41.080 --> 00:14:42.120
is sure to break out and become a hit.

00:14:43.519 --> 00:14:45.039
This is all thanks to you.

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:47.879
For making Peng Le Xuan split from within.

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:50.120
That's a ruthless move.

00:14:52.519 --> 00:14:53.480
You know,

00:14:53.600 --> 00:14:54.960
people used to say my methods

00:14:54.960 --> 00:14:56.639
were ruthless enough.

00:14:57.080 --> 00:14:58.840
But compared to you,

00:14:58.840 --> 00:15:00.399
I really feel I fall short.

00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:03.200
Good thing we're just business partners.

00:15:03.279 --> 00:15:04.960
If you were my opponent,

00:15:04.960 --> 00:15:06.639
I'd really be in for a world of hurt.

00:15:10.519 --> 00:15:11.279
Weiguo.

00:15:12.279 --> 00:15:13.639
Aren't you worried

00:15:13.639 --> 00:15:15.519
Lianbao will have a complete falling out with you?

00:15:16.720 --> 00:15:17.559
And what about you?

00:15:18.240 --> 00:15:19.080
Me?

00:15:28.399 --> 00:15:30.080
Li Lianbao,

00:15:30.200 --> 00:15:33.159
he always likes to take shortcuts.

00:15:33.519 --> 00:15:34.399
Sooner or later,

00:15:34.399 --> 00:15:36.200
he'll pay the price and learn his lesson.

00:16:06.399 --> 00:16:08.639
The ancient Greek philosopher Thales said,

00:16:08.919 --> 00:16:10.559
"The easiest thing in the world

00:16:10.559 --> 00:16:12.159
is to give advice to others.

00:16:12.360 --> 00:16:13.840
And the most difficult thing

00:16:13.840 --> 00:16:15.080
is to know oneself."

00:16:15.559 --> 00:16:16.799
They all hit the mark.

00:16:17.039 --> 00:16:18.000
No matter who it is,

00:16:18.320 --> 00:16:19.799
there's always a weakness to exploit.

00:16:20.000 --> 00:16:21.039
Everything went smoothly.

00:17:08.759 --> 00:17:10.000
The interior needs a major renovation.

00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:11.640
We'll reopen after the renovation is complete.

00:17:13.000 --> 00:17:13.720
