00:17:56.680 --> 00:17:57.359
Right.

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:02.559
Come on.

00:18:03.720 --> 00:18:04.960
Be careful.

00:18:05.240 --> 00:18:05.960
Take it slow.

00:18:16.519 --> 00:18:17.079
Slowly, slowly.

00:18:17.079 --> 00:18:18.160
Chunsheng, take it easy.

00:18:18.160 --> 00:18:19.119
Be really careful.

00:18:22.559 --> 00:18:23.599
Give him a hand. Catch it.

00:18:23.599 --> 00:18:24.640
Lend a hand and catch it.

00:18:24.839 --> 00:18:25.799
Grab it, grab it.

00:18:25.799 --> 00:18:26.599
Easy now.

00:18:27.400 --> 00:18:28.559
Slow down, slow down.

00:18:30.000 --> 00:18:32.640
This, this signboard has seen many years.

00:18:48.720 --> 00:18:49.440
Boss.

00:18:50.000 --> 00:18:52.359
We'll have someone send this signboard to your home later.

00:18:53.079 --> 00:18:54.720
Later, when Peng Le Xuan's renovation is done

00:18:54.720 --> 00:18:55.880
and it's time to reopen,

00:18:56.000 --> 00:18:58.000
