00:19:08.559 --> 00:19:10.240
He will no longer cook roast duck.

00:19:10.559 --> 00:19:11.640
Wait, personal reasons?

00:19:11.640 --> 00:19:13.319
What kind of personal reasons?

00:19:13.559 --> 00:19:15.319
So does that mean we won't get to eat

00:19:15.319 --> 00:19:16.359
Chunsheng's roast duck anymore?

00:19:16.359 --> 00:19:17.000
Exactly!

00:19:17.240 --> 00:19:19.160
If Chunsheng isn't making roast duck,

00:19:19.240 --> 00:19:22.480
can your place even still be called Peng Le Xuan?

00:19:23.079 --> 00:19:25.079
Don't worry, everyone.

00:19:25.240 --> 00:19:27.359
Although my boss won't be cooking roast duck,

00:19:27.359 --> 00:19:30.160
Peng Le Xuan has hired a new head chef.

00:19:30.240 --> 00:19:32.079
His skills are absolutely top-notch.

00:19:32.200 --> 00:19:34.119
You'll all be very satisfied.

00:19:34.480 --> 00:19:37.200
So who is this master chef?

00:19:37.319 --> 00:19:39.359
Next, let's welcome Peng Le Xuan's head chef

00:19:39.359 --> 00:19:40.640
