00:19:48.839 --> 00:19:50.119
You can call me Chef Sun.

00:19:51.000 --> 00:19:53.640
I am the fifth-generation successor of Southern City Sun's Roast Duck.

00:19:53.640 --> 00:19:54.720
I was also last year's

00:19:54.720 --> 00:19:57.079
runner-up in the Beijing Duck King Competition.

00:19:57.359 --> 00:19:58.319
From today onward,

00:19:58.559 --> 00:20:00.680
I will be the head chef at Peng Le Xuan.

00:20:01.000 --> 00:20:02.319
I welcome all our old neighbors

00:20:02.319 --> 00:20:04.160
to patronize us often and offer your feedback.

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:06.319
Please do patronize us, please do.

00:20:06.480 --> 00:20:09.480
Alright, next up is the tasting session.

00:20:09.559 --> 00:20:11.960
Then we can all sample Chef Sun's skills.

00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:14.119
We have to try it, right?

00:20:14.119 --> 00:20:15.839
See how it compares to our Chunsheng's.

00:20:15.839 --> 00:20:17.359
You're right. Let's taste it.

00:20:32.599 --> 00:20:34.319
Come on, come on.

00:20:34.400 --> 00:20:35.359
Everyone, have a taste.

00:20:35.759 --> 00:20:36.720
