00:20:36.839 --> 00:20:37.720
No, you all eat, you eat.

00:20:37.720 --> 00:20:38.599
You all go ahead and eat.

00:20:38.599 --> 00:20:40.480
Come on, make some room for me.

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:43.240
Come on, come on.

00:20:44.160 --> 00:20:45.839
