00:20:52.599 --> 00:20:54.880
I just like being with everyone, is that not allowed?

00:20:54.880 --> 00:20:55.319
Right, right.

00:20:55.319 --> 00:20:58.319
Fine, if you're happy, we're even happier, right?

00:20:58.319 --> 00:20:59.240
You eat, you eat, you eat.

00:20:59.240 --> 00:21:00.119
Pick up your chopsticks and eat.

