What chopsticks? There are no chopsticks.

00:21:02.640 --> 00:21:03.599
I'll get them for you.

00:21:03.599 --> 00:21:05.839
Today, my stomach isn't feeling too good.

00:21:05.839 --> 00:21:07.559
You all eat, don't let me bother you.

00:21:07.559 --> 00:21:07.920
Don't be like that.

00:21:07.920 --> 00:21:08.920
No, you should all eat.

00:21:08.920 --> 00:21:10.079
Come on, come on.

00:21:10.079 --> 00:21:10.880
Don't worry about me.

00:21:10.880 --> 00:21:13.400
