00:21:13.400 --> 00:21:15.079
Congratulations to Peng Le Xuan.

00:21:15.079 --> 00:21:16.720
For finding such a great chef.

00:21:17.119 --> 00:21:18.400
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

00:21:18.400 --> 00:21:19.240
Thank you, thank you.

00:21:19.240 --> 00:21:21.319
Thanks, thank you, thank you.

00:21:21.880 --> 00:21:22.559
Come on, come on.

00:21:22.559 --> 00:21:23.480
The duck is here!

00:21:23.799 --> 00:21:24.559
Duck.

00:21:24.799 --> 00:21:26.200
This big duck.

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:30.279
Plenty fat.

00:21:30.559 --> 00:21:33.039
Look at how well it's roasted.

00:21:33.599 --> 00:21:34.599
The color looks good.

00:21:34.599 --> 00:21:35.400
Of course.

00:21:35.599 --> 00:21:38.160
Crispy outside, tender inside, right?

00:21:41.079 --> 00:21:42.079
Look at that color.

00:21:42.079 --> 00:21:43.079
With one cut.

00:21:45.240 --> 00:21:46.880
Every slice has both fat and lean meat.

00:21:48.480 --> 00:21:49.240
Look.

00:21:49.359 --> 00:21:50.880
Look at how he holds the knife.

00:21:50.880 --> 00:21:51.880
Is that even a knife?

00:21:51.880 --> 00:21:53.720
It's like a calligraphy brush, like painting.

00:21:53.720 --> 00:21:55.640
With one stroke, the meat is 'painted' off.

00:21:56.079 --> 00:21:57.240
A whole plate is done.

00:21:57.240 --> 00:21:59.079
Crispy outside, tender inside.

00:21:59.079 --> 00:21:59.880
Look at this knife work.

00:21:59.880 --> 00:22:00.880
The knife work is excellent.

00:22:00.880 --> 00:22:01.119
Yes.

00:22:01.119 --> 00:22:01.839
Roasted perfectly.

00:22:01.839 --> 00:22:02.359
Good.

00:22:09.720 --> 00:22:12.599
That's why Peng Le Xuan hired him.

00:22:12.599 --> 00:22:13.359
Right.

00:22:14.240 --> 00:22:15.079
Good.

00:22:16.400 --> 00:22:17.920
Every slice has both fat and lean.

00:22:17.920 --> 00:22:19.000
Absolutely.

00:22:22.839 --> 00:22:23.400
Good.

00:22:30.720 --> 00:22:32.200
Every cut has meat and skin.

00:22:32.200 --> 00:22:33.400
I'll have a slice first.

00:22:39.880 --> 00:22:41.359
Quick, quick, here, here.

00:22:42.000 --> 00:22:43.240
Put it here, here, here.

00:22:43.839 --> 00:22:44.599
Okay, okay, okay.

00:22:45.319 --> 00:22:46.880
These pancakes are still warm.

00:22:48.000 --> 00:22:49.200
I've got to have a slice.

00:22:50.319 --> 00:22:51.279
Chef Sun.

00:22:51.960 --> 00:22:53.720
Tastes great, great.

00:22:53.720 --> 00:22:54.440
Authentic.

00:22:55.160 --> 00:22:56.079
Not bad, not bad.

00:22:56.079 --> 00:22:56.880
How is it?

00:22:57.000 --> 00:22:57.720
Not bad.

00:22:58.079 --> 00:23:01.720
Compared to Chunsheng's skills back in the day.

00:23:01.720 --> 00:23:02.839
They're on par.

00:23:02.839 --> 00:23:04.400
Both are great, authentic.

00:23:04.720 --> 00:23:07.599
No wonder he's a chef who won second place.

00:23:07.720 --> 00:23:08.880
The flavor is just different.

00:23:09.079 --> 00:23:11.799
Let me announce one more thing to everyone.

00:23:12.039 --> 00:23:13.079
Chef Sun.

00:23:13.079 --> 00:23:14.880
Will also represent our Peng Le Xuan.

00:23:14.880 --> 00:23:17.079
In the annual Duck King Competition.

00:23:17.079 --> 00:23:18.079
Great!

00:23:18.079 --> 00:23:18.799
Good!

00:23:19.720 --> 00:23:20.920
With skills like his.

00:23:20.920 --> 00:23:23.640
He's sure to bring back a big trophy.

00:23:24.480 --> 00:23:27.200
Didn't he get second place last year?

00:23:27.319 --> 00:23:28.640
So this year, when he goes.

00:23:28.640 --> 00:23:31.319
He's got to bring back the championship, right?

00:23:31.319 --> 00:23:32.839
Exactly, the championship.

00:23:32.839 --> 00:23:33.599
If he wins the championship.

00:23:33.599 --> 00:23:35.880
Then our Peng Le Xuan will be famous!

00:23:38.599 --> 00:23:40.559
Bring out our registration form too.

00:23:40.559 --> 00:23:43.359
Let everyone cheer for our Peng Le Xuan.

00:23:48.599 --> 00:23:49.160
Here.

00:23:49.359 --> 00:23:50.480
