00:24:21.480 --> 00:24:22.640
Chunsheng, Chunsheng.

00:24:22.640 --> 00:24:23.319
What's going on?

00:24:23.319 --> 00:24:24.359
What's happening?

00:24:24.359 --> 00:24:26.079
