00:27:20.440 --> 00:27:21.960
Dad, you're basically useless now.

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:23.200
Don't talk nonsense.

00:27:24.440 --> 00:27:25.880
Um, Boss...

00:27:26.480 --> 00:27:28.720
Do you think you could try to endure it a bit more?

00:27:29.519 --> 00:27:30.519
Overcome it.

00:27:31.720 --> 00:27:33.480
Overcome my foot! How can I overcome it?

00:27:33.480 --> 00:27:34.440
Right now,

00:27:35.039 --> 00:27:37.440
I can't even think about this stuff, okay?

00:27:37.680 --> 00:27:39.680
This is a psychological issue you have.

00:27:39.680 --> 00:27:40.960
You really need to overcome it.

00:27:40.960 --> 00:27:41.960
Overcome my foot!

00:27:41.960 --> 00:27:43.519
Didn't I just say?

00:27:43.960 --> 00:27:44.920
Don't worry about me.

00:27:44.920 --> 00:27:47.279
You should go review your lessons.

00:27:49.160 --> 00:27:50.960
Boss, calm down a bit.

00:27:52.279 --> 00:27:55.000
Look, Peng Le Xuan is in a crisis right now.

00:27:55.160 --> 00:27:57.440
That guy Sun stood us up.

00:27:57.440 --> 00:27:59.160
If we want to find another chef...

00:27:59.160 --> 00:28:00.599
