00:28:35.240 --> 00:28:37.160
Isn't this for the good of Peng Le Xuan?

00:28:37.160 --> 00:28:37.920
Yes.

00:28:38.279 --> 00:28:39.599
You don't worry about anything.

00:28:39.599 --> 00:28:40.920
You only know how to be a nice guy.

00:28:40.920 --> 00:28:42.559
So when problems arise, don't I have to solve them?

00:28:43.720 --> 00:28:45.160
So now I'm the useless one again?

00:28:45.920 --> 00:28:47.480
Solve it? You solved it...

00:28:47.599 --> 00:28:48.440
You solved it really well.

00:28:48.440 --> 00:28:49.480
Really, exceptionally well.

00:28:49.519 --> 00:28:51.240
You solved it so well Boss can't even touch a duck now.

00:28:51.240 --> 00:28:52.680
Bravo. Just great.

00:28:53.079 --> 00:28:54.559
Are you crazy?

00:29:04.759 --> 00:29:06.160
There's nothing wrong with you.

00:29:06.200 --> 00:29:08.079
Relax, there are no problems at all.

00:29:08.279 --> 00:29:09.920
And your health is improving.

00:29:12.160 --> 00:29:13.880
I came to have my tongue checked.

00:29:17.200 --> 00:29:19.000
This should just be a stress response.

00:29:19.720 --> 00:29:21.559
Have you suffered some kind of shock?

00:29:21.960 --> 00:29:23.559
Or some psychological trauma?

00:29:25.000 --> 00:29:26.759
I can't see any problems either.

00:29:27.480 --> 00:29:28.799
Your heart blood is a bit deficient.

00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:30.440
Stick out your tongue, let me see.

00:29:30.440 --> 00:29:32.960
Right, I think it's mainly my tongue.

00:29:37.720 --> 00:29:38.839
There's no problem.

00:29:38.839 --> 00:29:40.680
Pay more attention to your diet.

00:29:40.680 --> 00:29:41.599
Drink less alcohol.

00:29:41.799 --> 00:29:43.319
Exercise more when you can.

00:29:43.599 --> 00:29:44.799
At your age,

00:29:44.799 --> 00:29:46.480
you're not like a young person anymore.

00:29:53.160 --> 00:29:54.960
You went to see the doctor and get medicine...

00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:56.240
and you didn't even let me go with you.

00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:59.200
I was afraid you'd worry along with me.

00:30:10.799 --> 00:30:12.440
Did the doctor say...

00:30:12.440 --> 00:30:14.680
if there are side effects from taking anti-nausea medicine all the time?

00:30:15.079 --> 00:30:16.279
The doctor said it's fine.

00:30:41.599 --> 00:30:42.720
Twenty minutes.

00:30:43.480 --> 00:30:44.200
Take it out.

00:30:44.200 --> 00:30:44.720
Okay.

00:30:51.319 --> 00:30:52.000
No.

00:30:52.000 --> 00:30:54.039
No, no, take them all back, take them back.

00:30:54.319 --> 00:30:55.200
This still isn't okay?

00:30:55.200 --> 00:30:56.480
This smell, this...

00:30:57.640 --> 00:31:00.240
Dad, you can't even smell the duck?

00:31:00.759 --> 00:31:02.279
How about this? Can you look at it?

00:31:03.400 --> 00:31:04.160
What is it?

00:31:05.960 --> 00:31:07.920
Take it away, take it away now, I'm telling you.

00:31:08.440 --> 00:31:09.160
Jing'er, listen to me.

00:31:09.160 --> 00:31:09.920
Later, at home,

00:31:09.920 --> 00:31:11.240
anything related to this stuff,

00:31:11.240 --> 00:31:11.759
put it all away for me.

00:31:11.759 --> 00:31:13.039
Don't let me see it.

00:31:13.200 --> 00:31:15.079
No, you can't even look at it now?

00:31:15.160 --> 00:31:17.440
Then you definitely need to see a psychologist.

00:31:17.759 --> 00:31:18.599
See a psychologist for what?

00:31:18.599 --> 00:31:20.240
There's nothing wrong with my mind.

00:31:21.000 --> 00:31:23.680
Your son is asking you to go.

00:31:23.680 --> 00:31:25.319
Just go and see one.

00:31:25.720 --> 00:31:26.519
You should go.

00:31:27.200 --> 00:31:27.960
No.

00:31:28.279 --> 00:31:30.200
I've just been busy with my own stuff.

00:31:30.200 --> 00:31:31.920
How about you? How are your studies?

00:31:31.920 --> 00:31:32.680
I'm doing alright.

00:31:32.680 --> 00:31:33.480
You don't need to worry.

00:31:33.480 --> 00:31:34.000
You just focus on

00:31:34.000 --> 00:31:35.960
how to get over this mental hurdle of yours.

00:31:36.400 --> 00:31:39.000
No, don't worry about it, you go study.

00:31:49.039 --> 00:31:49.599
No, it's not okay.

00:31:49.599 --> 00:31:51.680
There are so many things to eat in this world.

00:31:52.119 --> 00:31:53.839
I just won't touch that thing.

00:31:56.839 --> 00:31:59.440
Turn on our range hood.

00:31:59.440 --> 00:32:01.279
Why do I still smell it now?

00:32:02.000 --> 00:32:02.680
Alright.

00:32:19.319 --> 00:32:19.920
Sister-in-law.

00:32:20.440 --> 00:32:20.920
Thank you.

00:32:20.920 --> 00:32:21.440
Thank you.

00:32:22.240 --> 00:32:23.000
Where's mine?

00:32:23.000 --> 00:32:23.839
Buy your own.

00:32:26.839 --> 00:32:28.680
Seeing your Boss like this now,

00:32:29.400 --> 00:32:30.519
makes me feel really awful.

00:32:31.920 --> 00:32:32.680
Sister-in-law.

00:32:32.880 --> 00:32:34.920
You just stay home and take good care of Boss.

00:32:35.440 --> 00:32:37.440
Don't let any other health issues come up.

00:32:37.759 --> 00:32:39.519
Leave the competition to me.

00:32:39.720 --> 00:32:40.920
Even if I have to risk my life,

00:32:40.920 --> 00:32:42.319
I'll find a good chef.

00:32:42.519 --> 00:32:44.559
and bring back the championship for this Duck King Competition.

00:32:46.160 --> 00:32:47.160
I think

00:32:47.160 --> 00:32:49.519
the one we can most count on now is still Boss.

00:32:49.799 --> 00:32:52.039
We must do everything we can to help him recover his skills.

00:32:52.640 --> 00:32:54.160
I think so too.

00:32:54.279 --> 00:32:55.400
I think no matter what,

00:32:55.400 --> 00:32:55.960
even if we have to force him,

00:32:55.960 --> 00:32:57.920
we have to force Dad to make roast duck again.

00:32:57.920 --> 00:32:58.960
I say, Feifei,

00:32:59.279 --> 00:33:01.079
is that any way to treat your own father?

00:33:01.480 --> 00:33:02.720
Peng Le Xuan's century-old craft,

00:33:02.720 --> 00:33:03.839
if it really ends like this,

00:33:04.000 --> 00:33:05.279
it would truly be a shame.

00:33:06.319 --> 00:33:07.720
I also want Boss's skills

00:33:07.720 --> 00:33:08.839
to recover quickly.

00:33:09.319 --> 00:33:10.720
But for this competition,

00:33:10.720 --> 00:33:12.000
it's definitely too late.

00:33:12.799 --> 00:33:14.759
Registration closes in four days.

00:33:15.000 --> 00:33:16.319
With Boss in his current state,

00:33:16.480 --> 00:33:17.920
he can't even touch a duck.

00:33:18.319 --> 00:33:19.680
If he wants to recover his skills,

00:33:19.680 --> 00:33:21.440
it'll take at least three to five months, no less.

00:33:22.799 --> 00:33:23.559
Sister-in-law.

00:33:24.039 --> 00:33:24.920
What's your take?

00:33:25.480 --> 00:33:27.839
I... I certainly don't want

00:33:27.839 --> 00:33:29.720
you all to leave your Boss behind.

00:33:29.720 --> 00:33:31.680
But I am truly worried

00:33:31.680 --> 00:33:33.440
he'll hold everyone back.

00:33:36.440 --> 00:33:37.440
Here's what I think.

00:33:37.759 --> 00:33:39.720
Those who believe in Boss, come with me

00:33:39.720 --> 00:33:40.759
to persuade him.

00:33:40.920 --> 00:33:42.599
As for the others,

00:33:42.920 --> 00:33:45.160
if they want to find another chef, go ahead.

00:33:45.720 --> 00:33:47.359
I say, Ma Weiguo,

00:33:47.839 --> 00:33:50.079
I just started liking you a couple of days ago,

00:33:50.079 --> 00:33:51.599
and you're starting to cause trouble again, huh?

00:33:51.720 --> 00:33:53.480
So it's me who doesn't believe in Boss?

00:33:53.559 --> 00:33:54.920
I'm the one creating conflict?

00:33:55.440 --> 00:33:57.440
I only said you *could* find another chef.

00:33:57.440 --> 00:33:59.200
*You're* the one talking about damaging unity.

00:33:59.599 --> 00:34:00.240
Alright.

00:34:00.240 --> 00:34:02.720
You two, stop picking at such childish wording.

00:34:02.720 --> 00:34:04.160
You're acting like kids.

00:34:04.240 --> 00:34:06.240
Let's split up and act, a double insurance.

00:34:06.240 --> 00:34:07.720
Isn't it all for Peng Le Xuan?

00:34:08.440 --> 00:34:11.000
See how well Tongtong speaks?

00:34:11.000 --> 00:34:12.199
Learn a thing or two.

00:34:14.480 --> 00:34:17.000
You two are a perfect match.

00:34:17.920 --> 00:34:18.559
Tongtong really knows how to talk.

00:34:18.559 --> 00:34:19.320
Who are you talking about?

00:34:19.320 --> 00:34:20.280
You two.

00:34:34.039 --> 00:34:35.599
That shop nearby,

00:34:36.079 --> 00:34:37.440
the one that was open for many years,

00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:38.679
the one that sold roast duck,

00:34:39.199 --> 00:34:40.440
just up and closed.

00:34:40.760 --> 00:34:42.679
Didn't they say it was being renovated?

00:34:42.760 --> 00:34:43.840
Don't listen to that.

00:34:44.159 --> 00:34:45.199
Just you wait.

00:34:45.360 --> 00:34:46.599
If it reopens,

00:34:46.760 --> 00:34:49.119
it definitely won't be the same as before.

00:34:49.440 --> 00:34:50.840
I know that shop.

00:34:50.840 --> 00:34:52.519
It was open for over a hundred years.

00:34:53.639 --> 00:34:55.400
What a pity.

00:34:56.000 --> 00:34:57.960
All these good old Beijing things,

00:34:57.960 --> 00:34:59.800
are slowly disappearing.

00:34:59.920 --> 00:35:01.960
The things our ancestors left behind,

00:35:01.960 --> 00:35:04.039
are all being lost now.

00:35:04.280 --> 00:35:04.800
You know,

00:35:04.800 --> 00:35:05.320
this...

00:35:33.159 --> 00:35:34.800
Finally willing to see me.

00:35:36.559 --> 00:35:38.760
Had to wait for you to calm down.

00:35:38.880 --> 00:35:40.840
So you wouldn't have a foul mouth again.

00:35:41.840 --> 00:35:42.920
My fault, my fault.

00:35:43.159 --> 00:35:44.400
I lost my composure.

00:35:45.440 --> 00:35:46.639
Let me punish myself with a drink first.

00:35:53.199 --> 00:35:54.760
But I have to say,

00:35:55.079 --> 00:35:56.840
you played a darn good hand.

00:35:57.960 --> 00:35:59.840
It's my own fault for not mastering the craft.

00:36:00.239 --> 00:36:01.400
I lost the bet, I accept the loss.

00:36:01.400 --> 00:36:03.199
This time, I admit defeat.

00:36:03.440 --> 00:36:04.360
Li Lianbao.

00:36:04.639 --> 00:36:07.239
You have no way out now.

00:36:09.079 --> 00:36:10.239
Not necessarily.

00:36:10.920 --> 00:36:12.960
Now, there are only

00:36:12.960 --> 00:36:14.320
four days left until the registration deadline.

00:36:14.639 --> 00:36:17.280
You want to find a capable chef now?

00:36:17.280 --> 00:36:18.440
It's definitely too late.

00:36:18.480 --> 00:36:20.280
If you miss this Duck King Competition,

00:36:20.440 --> 00:36:22.719
you'll miss the biggest wave of traffic.

00:36:23.199 --> 00:36:25.719
All your original plans will be delayed.

00:36:26.000 --> 00:36:28.000
One wrong step leads to another.

00:36:28.440 --> 00:36:29.440
Including

00:36:29.559 --> 00:36:32.039
Kevin's demands on you. You can't meet them now.

00:36:32.079 --> 00:36:33.360
So I advise you

00:36:33.360 --> 00:36:34.960
to face reality.

00:36:35.119 --> 00:36:36.119
Ridiculous.

00:36:36.440 --> 00:36:37.800
There's still time

00:36:37.800 --> 00:36:39.119
before Kevin's deadline.

00:36:39.480 --> 00:36:41.320
Who knows what will happen

00:36:41.440 --> 00:36:42.880
during that time?

00:36:43.000 --> 00:36:43.920
Me, personally,

00:36:43.920 --> 00:36:46.280
I never worry about things that haven't happened yet.

00:36:48.920 --> 00:36:50.960
Anyway, my offer still stands.

00:36:51.480 --> 00:36:53.400
I'll give you the best terms,

00:36:53.400 --> 00:36:55.119
as long as you hand over Peng Le Xuan to me.

00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:56.840
As for Kevin,

00:36:56.840 --> 00:36:58.039
I'll talk to him myself.

00:36:58.400 --> 00:37:01.000
I believe as long as it's a profitable business,

00:37:01.000 --> 00:37:02.440
he won't disagree.

00:37:02.920 --> 00:37:04.119
No way.

00:37:06.519 --> 00:37:07.920
Let me tell you again,

00:37:08.079 --> 00:37:08.960
it's not happening.

00:37:11.920 --> 00:37:13.519
I just don't get it.

00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:14.800
Why insist on pushing until

00:37:14.800 --> 00:37:16.559
you're battered and bruised?

00:37:17.079 --> 00:37:18.920
The price won't be the same then.

00:37:20.280 --> 00:37:22.440
You're thinking quite thoroughly for me.

00:37:22.840 --> 00:37:24.000
Not just for you,

00:37:24.199 --> 00:37:25.639
but also for Boss and Qiu'er.

00:37:28.920 --> 00:37:30.880
Whether you're sincere or not,

00:37:31.320 --> 00:37:32.400
I thank you.

00:37:33.159 --> 00:37:35.920
I'll take the heat from Boss and Qiu'er.

00:37:35.920 --> 00:37:38.320
And I'll carry my own burden too.

00:37:43.039 --> 00:37:45.280
Alright, no more work talk today.

00:37:45.440 --> 00:37:47.920
Since Director Dong is treating us so generously today,

00:37:48.199 --> 00:37:49.440
I won't hold back.

00:37:49.639 --> 00:37:50.960
Please, don't be polite. Enjoy.

00:37:58.199 --> 00:38:00.320
Your duck here is actually pretty good.

00:38:02.280 --> 00:38:03.440
Your mouth isn't bad either.

00:38:31.400 --> 00:38:32.559
That jerk.

00:38:33.400 --> 00:38:34.880
He even blocked me.

00:38:38.119 --> 00:38:39.480
Boss won't see me now.

00:38:39.480 --> 00:38:41.519
So I need you two to step in.

00:38:42.320 --> 00:38:42.960
This...

00:38:43.519 --> 00:38:45.239
might boost his sense of honor.

00:38:47.599 --> 00:38:48.519
Roast Duck King.

00:38:49.639 --> 00:38:52.480
Beijing's 8th Folk Roast Duck King Culinary Competition.

00:38:52.480 --> 00:38:54.480
Duck King Showdown. Welcome to the challenge.

00:38:55.480 --> 00:38:56.519
Okay, I get it.

00:38:56.519 --> 00:38:58.079
Anyway, when I go back, I need to make him realize

00:38:58.079 --> 00:38:59.320
that winning this Roast Duck King title

00:38:59.320 --> 00:39:00.679
is a matter of great prestige.

00:39:00.840 --> 00:39:01.480
Exactly.

00:39:01.599 --> 00:39:02.239
Alright.

00:39:02.920 --> 00:39:05.280
I think we could ask Grandpa Tong to help.

00:39:05.280 --> 00:39:06.960
Uncle Wang respects Grandpa Tong a lot.

00:39:06.960 --> 00:39:09.159
Maybe Grandpa Tong's words will work.

00:39:10.039 --> 00:39:11.159
That's also a way.

00:39:11.840 --> 00:39:12.559
But...

00:39:13.920 --> 00:39:15.280
This might also help.

00:39:17.079 --> 00:39:19.280
This... my dad lost this!

00:39:20.280 --> 00:39:21.559
How did you get it?

00:39:21.559 --> 00:39:22.800
Why so many questions?

00:39:24.400 --> 00:39:25.639
Some people

00:39:25.639 --> 00:39:27.320
really say one thing,

00:39:27.320 --> 00:39:28.840
but do another.

00:39:29.920 --> 00:39:30.679
Alright.

00:39:30.840 --> 00:39:32.199
Now that everyone knows,

00:39:32.320 --> 00:39:33.920
let's get moving.

00:39:34.599 --> 00:39:35.280
Roger that.

00:40:01.360 --> 00:40:02.159
What's wrong?

00:40:02.599 --> 00:40:03.840
Sorry, sorry.

00:40:04.280 --> 00:40:05.079
Sorry, sorry.

00:40:05.079 --> 00:40:05.639
What are you doing?

00:40:05.639 --> 00:40:06.280
Sorry, sir.

00:40:06.280 --> 00:40:07.920
I just want to talk to Sun Yanhui for a minute.

00:40:07.920 --> 00:40:09.079
I won't do anything else.

00:40:09.320 --> 00:40:10.039
Sorry, sir.

00:40:10.039 --> 00:40:11.800
Kitchen area. No unauthorized personnel.

00:40:11.800 --> 00:40:13.440
Our kitchen is not open to the public.

00:40:13.679 --> 00:40:14.840
Fine, fine. Then how about this:

00:40:15.000 --> 00:40:15.960
you call him out here,

00:40:15.960 --> 00:40:16.960
and I'll talk to him outside.

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:18.079
He's not here.

00:40:18.639 --> 00:40:19.559
Who are you kidding?

00:40:19.639 --> 00:40:20.719
Sir, if you're here to eat,

00:40:20.719 --> 00:40:21.559
I'll find you a seat.

00:40:21.559 --> 00:40:22.480
But please don't disturb

00:40:22.480 --> 00:40:23.960
our many other guests, okay?

00:40:24.719 --> 00:40:26.119
Dong Qian taught you this, right?

00:40:26.840 --> 00:40:27.400
Fine.

00:40:30.840 --> 00:40:31.599
Sorry, sorry.

00:40:31.599 --> 00:40:32.559
Sorry, everyone.

00:40:34.159 --> 00:40:35.400
Uncle Wang, look.

00:40:35.800 --> 00:40:36.960
How spirited you were back then.

00:40:36.960 --> 00:40:37.519
"In the future,

00:40:37.519 --> 00:40:39.639
I will definitely be

00:40:39.639 --> 00:40:41.320
the best roast duck chef in all of Beijing."